Deprecated. 

@Deprecated
public static class Configuration.InvocationBatching
extends Configuration.BooleanAttributeType
implements FluentConfiguration.InvocationBatchingConfig

Defines whether invocation batching is allowed in this cache instance, and sets up internals accordingly to allow use of this API.

Configuration reference, Serialized Form
